Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.86,0:25:07.40,Dragon Ball 3,,0,0,0,,{\i1}¡No escondas tu juventud!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.40,0:25:10.40,Dragon Ball 2,,0,0,0,, {\i1}Fushigi shitakute{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.40,0:25:10.40,Dragon Ball 3,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Quiero hacer lo misterioso{\i0}
